App-YTDL
========


INFO

Download single YouTube videos or choose videos from playlists/channels.
Before the download the script shows video infos and
lets you choose the video quality from the available qualities.
Instead of choosing the quality manually it is possible
to set and use preferred qualities.



INSTALLATION

    perl Makefile.pl
    make
    make test
    make install



HELP

yt-download -h




